text: Marko Kelemen (born 29 April 2000) is a Slovak footballer who plays for Kazincbarcikai SC, as a forward. ==Club career== Kelemen made his professional Fortuna Liga debut for Spartak Trnava against iClinic Sereď on 21 July 2019.FC Spartak a.s., Trnava - ŠKF iClinic Sereď 21.07.2019, futbalnet.sk ==References== ==External links== * FC Spartak Trnava official club profile * Futbalnet profile * * Fortuna Liga profile Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Slovak footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:FC DAC 1904 Dunajská Streda players Category:FC Spartak Trnava players Category:FC ViOn Zlaté Moravce players Category:Kazincbarcikai SC footballers Category:Slovak Super Liga players
